column2: "Oh, it's you. Thanks for the other day!"
"Camarotz is safe and sound now. There are a lot of different kinds in ARKS."
"I learned that it's okay to count on you guys, but not everyone has realized it yet."
"Recently, I haven't had any problems, but I'm hearing a lot of unsettling things."
"I mentioned it to that girl from before, but I don't expect anything to come of it."
"You, uh, don't need to concern yourself about it. Anyways, later!"
